#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/05_Runic_Gate-utils.cfg:29
msgid "Elri finds the traitor and kills him"
msgstr "Elri encuentra al traidor y lo mata"

#. [note]
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/05_Runic_Gate-utils.cfg:56
msgid "Drake Thrashers or Drake Enforcers can destroy weakened cave walls."
msgstr "Los Dracos Golpeadores o Dracos Ejecutores pueden destruir las paredes de cueva debilitadas."

#. [note]
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/05_Runic_Gate-utils.cfg:59
msgid "It is not necessary to kill every enemy here."
msgstr "No es necesario matar a todos los enemigos aquí."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:65
msgid "Sacrifice this drake?"
msgstr "¿Sacrificar a este draco?"

#. [option]
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:67
msgid "No"
msgstr "No"

#. [option]
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:82
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Sí"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:209
msgid "I am free once more!"
msgstr "¡Estoy libre una vez más!"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:217
msgid "Your flames are mine!"
msgstr "¡Tus llamas son mías!"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:282
msgid ""
"Herkarth! The Age of Drakes is upon us! We, the descendants of The Fire, "
"shall enslave all others and rule the world!"
msgstr ""
"¡Herkarth! ¡La Era de los Dracos ha llegado! ¡Nosotros, los descendientes del Fuego, esclavizaremos a todos los demás y dominaremos el mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Herkarth
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:287
msgid "The Fire burns stronger than ever!"
msgstr "¡El Fuego arde más fuerte que nunca!"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/scenarios/scenario-utils/07_Dragonheart-utils.cfg:292
msgid ""
"Forsooth! And we shall have our revenge on the dwarves for their vile "
"deception! They march toward the Ashen's Maw now, hoping to conquer our home,"
" but it is there that we will burn them to ashes!"
msgstr ""
"¡En verdad! ¡Y nos vengaremos de los enanos por su vil engaño! Marchan hacia la Fauce Cenicienta ahora, con la esperanza de conquistar nuestro hogar, ¡pero es allí donde los quemaremos hasta convertirlos en cenizas!"

#. [race], id=hidden_race
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/1AH_races.cfg:5
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/1AH_races.cfg:6
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/1AH_races.cfg:7
msgid "Unknown"
msgstr "Desconocido"

#. [race], id=hidden_race
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/1AH_races.cfg:9
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"The race of this unit cannot be revealed yet. You must discover it in the "
"game to be allowed to see its description."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"La raza de esta unidad aún no puede ser revelada. Debes descubrirla en el juego para poder ver su descripción."

#. [unit_type], id=Sky Drake Doody, race=drake
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dummy_Skydrake_Doody.cfg:7
msgid "Sky Drake"
msgstr "Draco del Cielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Sky Drake Doody, race=drake
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dummy_Skydrake_Doody.cfg:26
msgid ""
"The lightweight ceramic armor that the Sky Drakes wear is a symbol of their "
"rank, glazed silver to honor their connection to the air. As leaders of the "
"hunt, they are often away from their homes for long periods of time. Each "
"tries to bring as much game home as possible, competing to gain the respect "
"of their tribe and, just possibly, time with one of the closely-guarded drake"
" females."
msgstr ""
"La ligera armadura de cerámica que usan los Dracos del Cielo es un símbolo de su rango, esmaltada en plata para honrar su conexión con el aire. Como líderes de la caza, suelen estar lejos de sus hogares por largos períodos. Cada uno intenta traer la mayor cantidad de presas posible, compitiendo por ganar el respeto de su tribu y, tal vez, tiempo con una de las dracas hembras fuertemente protegidas."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dummy_Skydrake_Doody.cfg:59
msgid "slam"
msgstr "golpe"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dummy_Skydrake_Doody.cfg:68
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_dragon.cfg:43
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/dragonheart.cfg:42
msgid "fire breath"
msgstr "aliento de fuego"

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Bloodaxe, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Bloodaxe.cfg:5
msgid "Dwarvish Bloodaxe"
msgstr "Hacha de Sangre Enano"

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Bloodaxe, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Bloodaxe.cfg:19
msgid ""
"According to legend, the all-consuming bloodaxes were forged at the dawn of "
"time in the great stone-fires of Dhur Darihm, when all Irdya was still "
"drowned in flame and soot. It is with them that the first dwarves made war "
"against the troll-mother, laying low her people and forevermore claiming "
"dominion in the underearth. While the truth of this legend is a matter of "
"debate, battlefield reports leave no doubt that such weapons exist, and that "
"they confer great resilience upon their wielder. The dwarves’ few remaining "
"bloodaxes are jealously guarded, passed down from father to son and reclaimed"
" from the fallen even at great cost."
msgstr ""
"Según la leyenda, las hachas de sangre devoradoras fueron forjadas en el amanecer de los tiempos en las grandes hogueras de piedra de Dhur Darihm, cuando todo Irdya aún estaba sumergido en llamas y hollín. Con ellas los primeros enanos hicieron la guerra contra la madre troll, derribando a su pueblo y reclamando para siempre el dominio en el subsuelo. Aunque la veracidad de esta leyenda es debatible, los reportes de batalla no dejan duda de que tales armas existen y que confieren gran resistencia a su portador. Las pocas hachas de sangre restantes de los enanos son celosamente guardadas, transmitidas de padre a hijo y recuperadas de los caídos incluso a gran costo."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Bloodaxe.cfg:31
msgid "bloodaxe"
msgstr "hacha de sangre"

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Crownbearer, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Crownbearer.cfg:5
msgid "Dwarvish Crownbearer"
msgstr "Portador de Corona Enano"

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Crownbearer, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Crownbearer.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The Dwarvish Crownbearer is the bearer of the Underearth Crown, an unfinished"
" work of dwarvish runesmiths that grants the ability to cast forth ancient "
"runic magic."
msgstr ""
"El Portador de Corona Enano es el portador de la Corona del Subterráneo, una obra inconclusa de los runeros enanos que otorga la capacidad de lanzar antigua magia rúnica."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Crownbearer.cfg:25
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Ironbender.cfg:26
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_cavalry.cfg:38
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_rider.cfg:37
msgid "hammer"
msgstr "martillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Ironbender, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Ironbender.cfg:4
msgid "Dwarvish Ironbender"
msgstr "Doblador de Hierro Enano"

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Ironbender, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Ironbender.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Eager to explore the world in search of ancient and forgotten artifacts, the "
"Ironbender is a mostly lone survivor who will, nevertheless, embrace the "
"company of others if that helps to advance his cause. His travels and "
"artifacts collected in the span of his life have made him a tough adversary "
"for any foe foolish enough to pose an obstacle to his everlasting quest, "
"leading him away from the usual paths of the dwarvish people."
msgstr ""
"Ansioso por explorar el mundo en busca de artefactos antiguos y olvidados, el Doblador de Hierro es un solitario sobreviviente que, sin embargo, aceptará la compañía de otros si eso ayuda a avanzar su causa. Sus viajes y los artefactos recolectados a lo largo de su vida lo han convertido en un adversario duro para cualquier enemigo lo suficientemente tonto como para interponerse en su eterna búsqueda, alejándolo de los caminos habituales del pueblo enano."

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Protector, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Protector.cfg:5
msgid "Dwarvish Protector"
msgstr "Protector Enano"

#. [unit_type], id=Dwarvish Protector, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Protector.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Wearing mighty armour and a shield that have been passed on through "
"generations of Dwarves, the Dwarvish Protectors withstand even the most "
"vicious weapons and hottest flames. The Protectors are a rare caste of "
"Dwarves that have sworn allegiance to the lord of the clan to which they "
"belong and will die to protect him. As such, the Protectors are often seen in"
" the throne-halls of the imposing fortifications of the Dwarves. Standing "
"still for days on end and blessed with a stoic mind, they are often nearly "
"mistaken for the lifeless statues of stone that grace the inner halls made in"
" the likeness of the greatest warriors of yore. In times of war, Protectors "
"stand side by side with their clanmates and lords, their mighty shields "
"protecting not only themselves but also the warriors at their sides. Being "
"able to call forth lightning strikes with their voice alone, the enemy army "
"often scatters before a battle even takes place."
msgstr ""
"Usando poderosa armadura y un escudo que han sido transmitidos a través de generaciones de enanos, los Protectores Enanos resisten incluso las armas más viciosas y las llamas más calientes. Los Protectores son una rara casta de enanos que han jurado lealtad al señor del clan al que pertenecen y morirán para protegerlo. Por eso, los Protectores suelen verse en las salas del trono de las imponentes fortificaciones de los enanos. Permaneciendo inmóviles durante días enteros y bendecidos con una mente estoica, a menudo se les confunde con las estatuas sin vida de piedra que adornan los salones internos hechas a semejanza de los más grandes guerreros de antaño. En tiempos de guerra, los Protectores se paran hombro a hombro con sus compañeros de clan y señores, sus poderosos escudos protegiendo no solo a ellos mismos sino también a los guerreros a su lado. Al poder invocar rayos solo con su voz, el ejército enemigo a menudo se dispersa antes de que la batalla siquiera comience."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Protector.cfg:34
msgid "spear"
msgstr "lanza"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Protector.cfg:47
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_thunderlord.cfg:40
msgid "lightning"
msgstr "rayo"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Dwarvish_Protector.cfg:59
msgid "shield bash"
msgstr "golpe de escudo"

#. [unit_type], id=Elvish Bloodmaiden, race=elf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Elvish_Bloodmaiden.cfg:5
msgid "Elvish Bloodmaiden"
msgstr "Doncella de Sangre Elfa"

#. [unit_type], id=Elvish Bloodmaiden, race=elf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Elvish_Bloodmaiden.cfg:20
msgid ""
"For many races, it is highly unlikely to send their females into battle. For "
"certain elvish populations however, females called 'bloodmaiden' are sent "
"into battle as a rearguard whenever the elvish army suffered huge losses. "
"Only equipped with a long skirt and a sharp sword, the bloodmaidens then "
"blindly search for the ones that harmed their kin, finding them and turning "
"the battlefield into a pool of blood."
msgstr ""
"Para muchas razas es muy poco probable enviar a sus hembras a la batalla. Sin embargo, para ciertas poblaciones elfas, las hembras llamadas «doncellas de sangre» son enviadas a la batalla como retaguardia cuando el ejército elfo sufre grandes pérdidas. Equipadas solo con una falda larga y una espada afilada, las doncellas de sangre buscan ciegamente a aquellos que dañaron a su gente, los encuentran y convierten el campo de batalla en un charco de sangre."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/Elvish_Bloodmaiden.cfg:29
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_centurion.cfg:30
msgid "sword"
msgstr "espada"

#. [unit_type], id=Wanderer, race=hidden_race
#. [unit_type], id=Porter, race=hidden_race
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/The_Wanderer.cfg:27
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/The_Wanderer.cfg:119
msgid ""
"A mystical light. It is wandering around the Heartfangs since the inner fire "
"of the drakes of the Ashen's Maw weakened."
msgstr ""
"Una luz mística. Deambula por los Colmillos Profundos desde que el fuego interior de los dracos de la Fauce Cenicienta se debilitó."

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/The_Wanderer.cfg:37
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/The_Wanderer.cfg:83
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/The_Wanderer.cfg:129
msgid "missile"
msgstr "proyectil"

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/The_Wanderer.cfg:73
msgid "berdysch"
msgstr "berdysch"

#. [unit_type], id=Bear Cavalry, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_cavalry.cfg:5
msgid "Bear Cavalry"
msgstr "Caballería de Oso"

#. [unit_type], id=Bear Cavalry, race=dwarf
#. [unit_type], id=Bear Rider, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_cavalry.cfg:20
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_rider.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The bears of the valleys of the Mountains of Haag are one of the fiercest yet"
" tameable creatures of the Northlands. As both dwarves and bears inhabit "
"these mountains, it was just a matter of time the dwarves managed to tame "
"them. The Shorbear Clan was the first one to do so."
msgstr ""
"Los osos de los valles de las Montañas de Haag son una de las criaturas más feroces pero domesticables de las Tierras del Norte. Como tanto enanos como osos habitan estas montañas, solo era cuestión de tiempo que los enanos lograran domesticarlos. El Clan Shorbear fue el primero en hacerlo."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_cavalry.cfg:47
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_rider.cfg:46
msgid "bite"
msgstr "mordida"

#. [unit_type], id=Bear Rider, race=dwarf
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/bear_rider.cfg:5
msgid "Bear Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de Oso"

#. [unit_type], id=Clockwork Ballista, race=mechanical
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_ballista.cfg:5
msgid "Clockwork Ballista"
msgstr "Ballesta Mecánica"

#. [unit_type], id=Clockwork Ballista, race=mechanical
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_ballista.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Due to their low numbers, dwarves crafted machines, that support their cause."
" The dwarven-made Clockwork Ballista is a tool that has specifically crafted "
"in order to hunt down drakes. Equipped with heavy bolts, the ballista is able"
" to penetrate both armor and scales, which is the reason why the ballista is "
"crafted in huge numbers whenever the dwarves wage war against drakes. Imbued "
"with runic magic which controls it, it seems as though the clockwork ballista"
" has its own will."
msgstr ""
"Debido a su bajo número, los enanos fabricaron máquinas que apoyan su causa. La Ballesta Mecánica hecha por enanos es una herramienta específicamente creada para cazar dracos. Equipada con pesados virotes, la ballesta puede penetrar tanto armaduras como escamas, razón por la que se fabrican en grandes cantidades cada vez que los enanos declaran la guerra a los dracos. Imbuida con magia rúnica que la controla, parece como si la ballesta mecánica tuviera voluntad propia."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_ballista.cfg:30
msgid "crossbow"
msgstr "ballesta"

#. [unit_type], id=Clockwork Centurion, race=mechanical
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_centurion.cfg:4
msgid "Clockwork Centurion"
msgstr "Centurión Mecánico"

#. [unit_type], id=Clockwork Centurion, race=mechanical
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_centurion.cfg:18
msgid ""
"A huge mechanical steed, mounted by a mechanical unit, the centurion. Created"
" for the purpose of traversing long distances quickly, thereby nullifying the"
" biggest weakness of the dwarves; speed. They are capable sentinels in the "
"times of peace, and terrifying enemies as your opponents. Armed with dwarvish"
" made longsword, these automatons are a force to be reckoned with."
msgstr ""
"Un enorme corcel mecánico montado por una unidad mecánica, el centurión. Creado con el propósito de recorrer largas distancias rápidamente, anulando así la mayor debilidad de los enanos: la velocidad. Son centinelas capaces en tiempos de paz y enemigos aterradores como oponentes. Armados con una espada larga hecha por enanos, estos autómatas son una fuerza a tener en cuenta."

#. [unit_type], id=Clockwork Dragon, race=mechanical
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_dragon.cfg:5
msgid "Clockwork Dragon"
msgstr "Dragón Mecánico"

#. [unit_type], id=Clockwork Dragon, race=mechanical
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_dragon.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The peak of dwarvish engineering, the clockwork dragon. A work of outstanding"
" artistry of a skilled arcanister, created with the mastery and might of the "
"runes. This behemoth creature of metal and steel has the power to pierce "
"through a dozen soldiers with its beak, and its firepower is not to be "
"meddled with. Many underestimate and mock this creation for its attempt to "
"imitate a real dragon, and many realise too late how foolish they were..."
msgstr ""
"La cima de la ingeniería enana, el dragón mecánico. Una obra de arte sobresaliente de un arcanista habilidoso, creada con la maestría y el poder de las runas. Esta criatura descomunal de metal y acero tiene el poder de atravesar una docena de soldados con su pico, y su potencia de fuego no debe ser subestimada. Muchos subestiman y se burlan de esta creación por su intento de imitar a un dragón real, y muchos se dan cuenta demasiado tarde de lo tontos que fueron..."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_dragon.cfg:33
msgid "beak"
msgstr "pico"

#. [line_damage]
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/clockwork_dragon.cfg:53
msgid ""
"This unit deals half damage to the unit that is standing behind the attacked "
"unit."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad inflige la mitad de daño a la unidad que se encuentra detrás de la unidad atacada."

#. [unit_type], id=Dragonheart, race=drake
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/dragonheart.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The dragonheart is the link between dragons and drakes. Being a direct "
"descendant of dragons, the blood of the dragons is flowing through his veins."
" In comparison to the drakes, the descendants of the dragonheart, the "
"dragonheart is able to control his magical inner fire to unleash his great "
"powers. It is said, that dragonhearts are living inside the magma chambers of"
" volcanoes and that they are the ones keeping the volcanoes active for the "
"heat they are emerging can melt both stone and steel with ease."
msgstr ""
"El corazón de dragón es el vínculo entre dragones y dracos. Al ser un descendiente directo de los dragones, la sangre de los dragones corre por sus venas. En comparación con los dracos, sus descendientes, el corazón de dragón es capaz de controlar su fuego interior mágico para desatar sus grandes poderes. Se dice que los corazones de dragón viven dentro de las cámaras de magma de los volcanes y que son ellos quienes mantienen los volcanes activos, pues el calor que emanan puede derretir tanto la piedra como el acero con facilidad."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/dragonheart.cfg:33
msgid "battle claws"
msgstr "garras de batalla"

#. [unit_type], id=Gryphon Scout, race=gryphon
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_scout.cfg:5
msgid "Gryphon Scout"
msgstr "Explorador Grifo"

#. [unit_type], id=Gryphon Scout, race=gryphon
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_scout.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Gryphon Scouts are mostly elderly dwarves that ride an especially fast "
"gryphon to catch up with fleeing prey or to espy the foothills of the great "
"mountains of the Northlands. The riders are often old dwarves not because "
"they are particularly experienced, but because their life is expendable, as "
"the flights of Gryphon Scouts are often a very dangerous undertaking."
msgstr ""
"Los Exploradores Grifo son en su mayoría enanos ancianos que montan un grifo especialmente rápido para alcanzar presas en fuga o espiar las estribaciones de las grandes montañas de las Tierras del Norte. Los jinetes suelen ser enanos viejos no porque sean particularmente experimentados, sino porque su vida es prescindible, ya que los vuelos de los Exploradores Grifo suelen ser una empresa muy peligrosa."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_scout.cfg:31
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_thunderlord.cfg:31
msgid "claws"
msgstr "garras"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_scout.cfg:41
msgid "net"
msgstr "red"

#. [unit_type], id=Gryphon Thunderlord, race=gryphon
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_thunderlord.cfg:5
msgid "Gryphon Thunderlord"
msgstr "Señor del Trueno Grifo"

#. [unit_type], id=Gryphon Thunderlord, race=gryphon
#: ./Ashen_Hearts/units/gryphon_thunderlord.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The bond between the Gryphon Thunderlords and their gryphons is unexcelled, "
"forming a steady unity. Being enchanted with runic armor, these gryphons are "
"able to reach the sky with ease. Once atop the clouds themselves, the Gryphon"
" Thunderlords cast appalling lightning strikes to decimate and demoralize "
"their foes."
msgstr ""
"El vínculo entre los Señores del Trueno Grifo y sus grifos es inigualable, formando una unidad sólida. Encantados con armadura rúnica, estos grifos pueden alcanzar el cielo con facilidad. Una vez en lo alto de las nubes, los Señores del Trueno Grifo lanzan aterradores rayos para diezmar y desmoralizar a sus enemigos."
